    <title><![CDATA[MongoDB安装脚本]]></title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2014/05/19/mongodb-install-shell/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2014/05/19/mongodb-install-shell/</id>
    <published>2014-05-19T07:12:46.000Z</published>
    <updated>2014-05-19T07:25:39.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="MongoDB安装脚本">MongoDB安装脚本</h1>
<ul>
<li>安装并启动mongodb</li>
</ul>
<p>将以下内容保存为shell脚本并招行</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre>1
2
3
4
5
6
7
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="shebang">#!/bin/bash</span>
wget http://fastdl.mongodb.org/linux/mongodb-linux-x86_64-<span class="number">2.6</span>.<span class="number">1</span>.tgz
tar xvf mongodb-linux-x86_64-<span class="number">2.6</span>.<span class="number">1</span>.tgz  
mkdir -p /data/mongodb/logs
mkdir -p /data/mongodb/data
mv mongodb-linux-x86_64-<span class="number">2.6</span>.<span class="number">1</span> /data/mongodb
ulimit -n <span class="number">2048</span> && /data/mongodb/mongodb-linux-x86_64-<span class="number">2.6</span>.<span class="number">1</span>/bin/mongod --logpath /data/mongodb/logs/mongo.log --dbpath /data/mongodb/data --bind_ip <span class="number">127.0</span>.<span class="number">0.1</span> --fork
</pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>bind_ip: 只允许通过该IP连接<br>logpath: 日志路径<br>dbpath:  数据文件路径</p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li>运行mongodb客户端</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre>1
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre>/data/mongodb/mongodb-linux-x86_64-<span class="number">2.6</span>.<span class="number">1</span>/bin/mongo
</pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>创建数据库、用户和索引</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre>1
2
3
4
5
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre>use mydatabase
db.createUser( { <span class="string">"user"</span> : <span class="string">"your_name"</span>,
                 <span class="string">"pwd"</span>: <span class="string">"your_password"</span>,
                 <span class="string">"roles"</span> : [ <span class="string">"readWrite"</span>] 
               });
</pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
